text: Domenica Ananias Cancino (born 18 August 1998) is a Chilean field hockey player. Ananias has represented Chile at both junior and senior levels. She made her junior debut at the 2016 Pan-Am Junior Championship, and her senior debut two years later in a test series against Canada. ==References== Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Chilean female field hockey players
